com.jrefinery.chart.combination
Interface AxisRange

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractAxisRange
public interface AxisRange

Interface used by CombinedPlot to represent the min/max range of an axis. This allows general algorithms to operate on dates and numerical ranges.
